reviewText: No conceptual explanation. Trivial examples taken. I was expecting some serious, realistic, moderately complex examples. A waste of time.
The course content was good but waited half an hour and the cloud workspace was still "Starting your cloud workspace, please wait" so in the end I set up my own local enviroment instead.
Very short course, but it takes the point
good to learn something in coursera.
Its a good one for real time practice
